snippet.textDisplay: So much nostalgia with this theme. I remember coming to this store like every week to see what new titles hit the digital shelves. If it wasn't for the Wii (and in turn, the Wii Shop Channel), I feel like my experiences with video games would be so much different now. I still remember how exciting it was playing A Link to the Past and Ocarina of Time for the first times with this service!
